umbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/monday-final-ratings-dec-5-2016/|title=\u2018The Voice\u2019 and '2 Broke Girls' adjust up, 'Christmas Light Fight' 'Conviction' adjust down: Monday final ratings|last=Porter|first=Rick|date=December 6, 2016|work=TV by the Numbers|accessdate=December 6, 2016}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary = When the kids put a hole in the wall with their rowdy play, Adam's and Andi's different approaches to parenting are put to the test. Each tries to get the kids to turn on each other and identify the culprit, but the resolve of their children is surprisingly strong.\n |LineColor = 10519C\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 7\n |EpisodeNumber2 = 7\n |Title = Winter Has Come\n |DirectedBy = James Burrows\n |WrittenBy = Farhan Arshad\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|12|12}}\n |Viewers = 6.62<ref name=\"1.07\">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/monday-final-ratings-dec-12-2016/|title=\u2018Timeless\u2019 and 'Great Christmas Light Fight' adjust down: Monday final ratings|last=Porter|first=Rick|work=TV by the Numbers|date=December 13, 2016|accessdate=December 13, 2016}}</ref>\n |ShortSummary = To get out of his usual Christmas chores, Adam convinces Andi's parents to host a family Christmas at their home in Virginia Beach. He orders all of the kids' gifts online and has them delivered to Virginia Beach, but his plan backfires when they get snowed in on the day of their trip. Forced to improvise, Adam has to pull off a \"Christmas miracle\" to avoid disappointing the kids and angering Andi.\n |LineColor = 10519C\n}}\n{{Episode list\n |EpisodeNumber = 8\n |EpisodeNumber2 = 8\n |Title = Adam Steps Up\n |DirectedBy = Pamela Fryman\n |WrittenBy = Gregg Mettler\n |OriginalAirDate = {{Start date|2016|12|19}}\n |Viewers = 6.17<ref name=\"1.08\">{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/daily-ratings/great-christmas-light-fight-finale-adjusts-down-monday-final-ratings/|title=\u2018Great Christmas Light Fight\u2019 finale adjusts